/ssl-certs.py --help
usage: ssl-certs.py [-h] [--list] [--host HOST] [--debug]

Ansible dynamic inventory

optional arguments:
  -h, --help   show this help message and exit
  --list       List instances (default: True)
  --host HOST  Get all the variables about a specific instance
  --debug

EXAMPLE
ansible -i ~/ssl-certs.py --list-hosts wild_gabiacns_com
ansible -i ~/ssl-certs.py --list-hosts wild_gabiacns_com_firstmall_addition
